import React from "react"
import {Stack} from 'react-bootstrap'
import Item from "./item"
import Search from "./Search"
import Filter from "./Filter"

export default function Home(){
    return (
        <>
        <Search />
        <Filter />
        <Stack direction="horizontal" gap={3}>
            <Item></Item>
            <Item></Item>
        </Stack>
        </>
        
        
    );
}
